<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 3 (Marta) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>遅かったね、エミル。
今日はどこ行ってたの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're late, Emil.
Where were you today?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん。
ちょっとルビアの家に行ってきたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh. I just had to go to Rubia's house for a bit.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>えぇぇぇぇぇ！！？
女の子の家に！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whaaaaa?!!
You went to a GIRL'S house?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あっ、うん。でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uh, yeah. But...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>信じられない！！
きっと脅迫でもして呼び寄せたのね！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't believe this!!
She must have threatened you to get you there!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちょ、ちょっとマルタ！
僕の話を……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Wait a second, Marta!
Listen to what I'm...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>これは女の子の合戦よ！
雌雄を決する合戦なんだから！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is a girls' battle!
A battle to decide who will be victorious!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
